(8-Feb-2008)
- Fixed DSIs in the DMG plugin.

52.29 (7-Feb-2008)
- Added RELOADPLUGINS/S option to MountDiskImage.
- Fixed several bugs in the error reporting routines.
- DMG plugin for .dmg files.

52.28 (7-Feb-2008)
- Rewritten and improved diskimage.device with plugin support (plugins are
  stored in DEVS:DiskImage).
- CISO plugin for reading .cso files.
- DMS, IPF, XAD and XPK now implemented as plugins.

52.27 (4-Feb-2008)
- Fixed placement of icon when DiskImageGUI window is iconified.
- IDiskImage not dropped on exit (DiskImageGUI).
- Added .raw support.
- Disabled the (not working) .uif support.

52.26 (14-Jan-2008)
- Unit process names (diskimage.device:<unit number>).
- Added default tool (MountDiskImage) and DRIVE tooltype to def_??? icons.
- D64FileSystem 0.3.
- Fixed CDFileSystem related problem (CDFileSystem doesn't seem to like that
  diskimage.device HD_SCSICMD only supports a few of the commands required by
