- Better handling of HD_SCSICMD and support for the 'read capacity' command.
- The device now uses NP_NotifyOnDeathMessage for its units.
- Added .uif support (untested).
- New icons by Martin "Mason" Merz.
- D64FileSystem 0.2 (see d64filesystem.readme).

52.24 (26-Oct-2007)
- Simple HD_SCSICMD implementation that supports only the 'inquiry' and
