- Added KEEPOPEN option to MountDiskImage.

52.22 (10-Oct-2007)
- Added Italian catalogs.
- Added new icons by Mason.
- Implemented AbortIO in the device.

52.21 (12-Aug-2007)
- Updated Finnish catalog.
