- Improved TD_GETGEOMETRY handling.
- Fixed locale support in GUI (wasn't working before).
- Added doubleclick handling for unit/drive list in GUI (insert/eject).
- Added gadget help texts for button bar in GUI.

52.12 (19-Jun-2007)
- Rewritten and improved .ipf support.
- Added a simple install script.

52.11 (17-Jun-2007)
- Supports compressed .ipf files (xad/xpk).
- Filters out readmes and some other non-mountable files from xad archives
